title: American Horror Story Weekly Wednesday Live Stream
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: So I know this is off-topic, but I love your lipstick! Actually, it's always on point for all your videos. I'm such a sucker for the red vampy look & am always in search for the best red lipsticks to buy. Sadly, my poor wallet suffers from this addiction. lol. Also, I have got to get one of those Camp Redwood shirts. That is awesome!

We don’t know Mr Jingles is OUR killer, he’s just A killer.  And why aren’t we talking about Brooke being attacked by and surviving the Night Stalker!? That trailer is chock full of clues, and I’m so excited for Mitch Pileggi (our fourth X-Files connection, too.)
P.S. I have notes!
Hell yes to having Sarah Michelle Gellar join AHS
I NEEEEEDDDD THIS SHIRT!!!! OMG ILY MARY!!

Sorry I missed the stream. But we don't know who Mr jingles is under the mask. So I'm still looking forward to the theory video tomorrow. 👍 Plus I kind of had a thought. What if Leslie Grossman's character is a survivor from the massacre from the past and is now running the camp.
